Administration

Fully customizable controls for branding, managing projects, organizations, vendors, users and more.

Customizable branding for users, organizations and the entire CUBE Portal

  • Users can customize their profile, theme and even certain UI elements like viewer layouts
  • Invite multiple organizations into your portal, assign their company logos and other elements
  • Connect your own custom domain and provide a branded experience to internal users as well as external vendors

Granular settings for every aspect of administrative control

  • At a Portal level, we have Portal settings, where global admins can control various aspects of how users interact with the CUBE platform in general.
  • Next, there's Project settings to control and administer things at a Project level. Changes made here are specific to only the particular project.
  • Going deeper, users can control aspects of localized spaces as well as permissions at a folder level.
